{"tid":1251684,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"醜事傳千里，輿論救義士（2）","createTime":"2019-06-22T15:47:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-23T05:52:50.000Z","uid":191290,"like":41,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"92c3ea2c72d602ef87990c74bf4b4d55992e58b9","tid":1251684,"uid":191290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T15:47:29.000Z","msg":"好，我終於上水。612發惡夢之後精神一直都唔係太好，尋日發完夢再處理埋啲私人嘢，搞到而家先有時間開group<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />梳啊。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>原post:</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>621 醜事傳千里，輿論救義士。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1244725/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1244725/page/1</a></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">此戰略執行方法要拋頭露面，因此如果你唔怕畀人點相，自問夠理性、EQ高、辯才好、轉數快嘅，請你立撚刻入嚟。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">另外，唔想露面但你自問足智多謀，天馬行空有鬼才，亦歡迎你加入一齊研究。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">現階段暫時只有概念，詳細實行方法未完善，歡迎畀意見。我哋亦會商討一啲行動原則，只要唔打破原則，可以任你發揮。</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4df1669093d4efc1f21d7d80825732283b997068","tid":1251684,"uid":191290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T15:48:49.000Z","msg":"入咗group嘅戰友，我會聽日先加入討論，今日好攰，會早啲瞓，請見諒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76af7a09ac742d02ac983953b845cfea08edf75c","tid":1251684,"uid":191290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T15:49:31.000Z","msg":"推啊推"},{"pid":"cf7b3ace9631e74d844c8925cbf233e97215e265","tid":1251684,"uid":191290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T15:49:50.000Z","msg":"上熱門就可以瞓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8f72cac96983bb5c555ce500aedb3119eb4716a","tid":1251684,"uid":191290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T15:50:08.000Z","msg":"人嚟啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"530e4d9ec98215ef7ff916862fdec72f8bb5b449","tid":1251684,"uid":191290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T15:51:06.000Z","msg":"見到幫手推啊喂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41cb80301eb68e48291e61c4d99cdb2a12617ee1","tid":1251684,"uid":264676,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T16:01:15.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，借個位黎擺下，希望更多人見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1251015/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1251015/page/1</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cu2oJOS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCu2oJOS.jpg&h=a799cc9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ASGkL2d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FASGkL2d.jpg&h=daa617d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/